source.name: Almanac API - Ranking by Geography Type within a State
source.description: This API is designed to find the rankings by any geography type within the state with a specific census metric (population or household) and ranking metric (any of the metrics from provider, demographic, technology or speed). Only the top ten and bottom ten rankings would be returned through the API if the result set is greater than 500; otherwise full ranking list be returned.
